---
title: Sequence Diagram - Login Staf
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Staf as Staf Hotel
    participant UI as Halaman /login
    participant Sup as Supabase Auth
    participant DB as Tabel user_roles + roles
    participant App as Aplikasi StayManager

    Staf->>UI: Input email + password
    UI->>Sup: signInWithPassword(email, password)
    Sup-->>UI: { user, session, error }
    alt Kredensial salah
        UI-->>Staf: Tampilkan pesan error
    else Kredensial valid
        UI->>DB: SELECT role.name, role.permissions FROM user_roles WHERE user_id = ?
        DB-->>UI: roles[] + permissions[]
        UI->>UI: Simpan session + permissions di Context
        UI->>App: redirect ke /dashboard
        App-->>Staf: Tampilkan sidebar sesuai permissions
    end
